ww.nfl.com/news/story/0ap3000001037458/article/lions-release-rb-theo-riddick-after-six-seasons|website=NFL.com|date=July 27, 2019|accessdate=July 27, 2019}}</ref>\n|- \n| August 4\n| [[Deontez Alexander]]\n| Wide receiver\n| Released\n| \n| <ref name=\"August 4\"/>\n|- \n| August 27\n| [[Zach Zenner]]\n| Running back\n| Released\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|first=David|last=Birkett|title=Detroit Lions release Zach Zenner, likely going light at RB position|url=https://www.freep.com/story/sports/nfl/lions/2019/08/27/detroit-lions-roster-zach-zenner/2134498001/|website=Detroit Free Press|date=August 27, 2019|accessdate=August 28, 2019}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Re-signings===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Detroit Lions|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Date\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Detroit Lions|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Player\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Detroit Lions|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Position\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Detroit Lions|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Contract\n!style=\"{{NFLPrimaryStyle|Detroit Lions|year=2019|border=2}}\"| Source\n|-\n| February 13\n| [[Don Muhlbach]]\n| [[Long snapper]]\n| 1 year / $1.12 million\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.detroitlions.com/news/lions-re-sign-ls-don-muhlbach |title=Lions re-sign LS Don Muhlbach |work=Detroit Lions |date=February 13, 2019 |accessdate=February 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| March 1\n| [[Romeo Okwara]]\n| [[Defensive end]]\n| 2 years / $6.8 million\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nfl.com/news/story/0ap3000001020154/article/lions-de-romeo-okwara-agree-on-2year-contract |title=Lions, DE Romeo Okwara agree on 2-year contract |work=NFL.com |first=Grant |last=Gordon |date=March 1, 2019 |accessdate=March 1, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| March 12\n| [[Zach Zenner]]\n| [[Running back]]\n| 1 year / \u2013\n| <ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.detroitlions.com/news/lions-re-sign-rb-zach-zenner-to-one-year-contract-extension |title=Lions re-sign RB Zach Zenner to one-year contract extension |work=Detroit Lions |date=March