in |title=Seahawks sign cornerback Jamar Taylor, Fullback Nick Bellore & Guard Marcus Martin |work=Seattle Seahawks |first=John |last=Boyle |date=May 9, 2019 |accessdate=May 11, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| May 15\n| [[Levine Toilolo]]\n| Tight end\n| UFA\n| [[San Francisco 49ers]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.49ers.com/news/49ers-sign-te-levine-toilolo-waive-s-cameron-glenn |title=49ers Sign TE Levine Toilolo, Waive S Cameron Glenn |work=San Francisco 49ers |date=May 15, 2019 |accessdate=May 23, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| June 10\n| [[Connor Cook]]\n| [[Quarterback]]\n| Released\n| \n| <ref name=Bowanko-Fales/>\n|- \n| June 14\n| [[Michael Roberts (American football)|Michael Roberts]]\n| Tight end\n| Released\n| [[Green Bay Packers]]\n| <ref name=\"Roberts waived\">{{cite web|first=Dave|last=Birkett|title=Detroit Lions waive TE Michael Roberts after trade with Patriots voids|url=https://www.freep.com/story/sports/nfl/lions/2019/06/14/michael-roberts-detroit-lions-patriots/1459795001/|website=Detroit Free Press|date=June 14, 2019|accessdate=June 26, 2019}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Logan|last=Reardon|title=Packers claim ex-Lions TE Roberts after voided trade|url=http://www.nfl.com/news/story/0ap3000001034027/article/packers-claim-former-lions-te-michael-roberts|website=NFL.com|date=June 17, 2019|accessdate=June 26, 2019}}</ref>\n|- \n| July 27\n| [[Theo Riddick]]\n| [[Running back]]\n| Released\n| [[Denver Broncos]]\n| <ref>{{cite web|first=Jeremy|last=Bergman|title=Lions release RB Theo Riddick after six seasons|url=http://www.nfl.com/news/story/0ap3000001037458/article/lions-release-rb-theo-riddick-after-six-seasons|website=NFL.com|date=July 27, 2019|accessdate=July 27, 2019}}</ref>\n|- \n| August 4\n| [[Deontez Alexander]]\n| Wide receiver\n| Released\n| \n| <ref name=\"August 4\"/>\n|- \n| August 27\n| [[Zach Zenner]]\n| Running back\n| Released\n| \n| <ref>{{cite web|first=David|last=Birkett|title=Detroit Lions release Zach Zenner, likely going light at RB position|url=